snippet.title: Top 10 Animated Superhero Movies
snippet.description:
Live-action superhero movies are now a Hollywood staple, but there are plenty of animated adventures that are just as impressive. Join http://www.WatchMojo.com as we count down our picks for the top 10 animated superhero movies.Check us out at http://www.Twitter.com/WatchMojo, http://instagram.com/watchmojo and http://www.Facebook.com/WatchMojo.

Special thanks to our users Scott Frank Neve II, Brian Silva, CaptainSandwich, marioarias and Chris Ashton for submitting the idea on our Suggestions Page at WatchMojo.com/suggest

Check out the voting page here, 
http://watchmojo.com/suggest/The%20Top%2010%20Greatest%20Animated%20Superhero%20Films
If you want to suggest an idea for a WatchMojo video, check out our interactive Suggestion Tool at http://www.WatchMojo.com/suggest :)

We have T-Shirts!  Be sure to check out http://www.WatchMojo.com/store for more info. 

WatchMojo is a leading producer of reference online video content, covering the People, Places and Trends you care about.
We update DAILY with 2-3 Top 10 lists, Origins, Biographies, Versus clips on movies, video games, music, pop culture and more!
